<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> / Es hat Hans <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Hohenheim / ein gütlıch ſteen beredt / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l3"><expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns vnd den
                                <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / vnd
                            <expan>Eberhart<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Tünfelt vnd den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l4">ſeinen / biʒ aus ſant Johans tag cʒü Sübenden / vnd
                        das ſol auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l5">den freÿtag als <expan>morge<ex>n</ex></expan> angeen
                        / . Da wiʒʒ dich nach cʒerıchten / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l6">Doch ob vns das Hans <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Hohenheim in Acht <expan>tage<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex>püt</expan> ſo <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> es </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l7">wıder ab / vnd ob er vns des nicht
                                <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>pewt</expan> / ſo ſol er vns in
                                <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l8">Acht <expan>tage<ex>n</ex></expan> die
                                <expan>beſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſchıcken
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Eberharts <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Tünfelt <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l9">welıche die ſeinen ſein / mit den das gütlıch ſteen
                        ſein ſol / . vnd ob Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l10">alſlang <del rend="strikethrough">aſſe </del> awſſen
                        beleibt/ was vns <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> Hans
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hohenheim <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_r1l11">empewtet / das <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        dich <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ du dıch mit
                            <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_109_line_1576567404445_1176"><expan>geſelle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        darnach <expan>cʒerıcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvıſſeſt /
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ṽ . <expan>An<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Pentecoſt<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_109" id="54r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan>
<expan>Heidnab<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, es hat Hans <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Hohenheim ein gütlich steen beredt <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns und
                        den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und <expan>Eberhart<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Tünfelt und den seinen biz aus <app><note><q type="date">sant Johans tag
                            czü sübenden</q>24.06.1410</note></app> und das sol <app><note><q type="date">auf den freytag als <expan>morge<ex>n</ex></expan></q>09.05.1410</note></app>
                        angeen, da wizz dich nach cze richten. Doch ob uns das Hans
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hohenheim in acht
                            <expan>tage<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex>püt</expan>, so <expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> es wider
                        ab; und ob er uns des nicht <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>pewt</expan>, so sol er uns
                        in <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> acht <expan>tage<ex>n</ex></expan> die
                                <expan>beschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> schicken
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Eberharts <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Tünfelt <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, weliche die seinen sein, mit den das
                        gütlich steen sein sol. Und ob ir alslang awssen beleibt, was uns
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> Hans <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Hohenheim <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> empewtet, das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir dich <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz du dich mit
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geselle<ex>n</ex></expan> darnach <expan>czericht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wissest. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>pentecost<ex>en</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
